Packages 
Package Description
org.hck.annotations
Package contains classes related to custom annotations built to be used in this framework.
org.hck.constants
Package contains classes related to framework constants.
org.hck.driver
Package contains classes related to WebDriver initialisation and management.
org.hck.enums
Package contains Enums that is used across the entire framework.
org.hck.exceptions
Package contains classes related to user defined exceptions
org.hck.factories
Package contains classes related to factory models.
org.hck.helpers
Package contains classes related to selenium actions.
org.hck.listners
Package contains classes related to different listeners used in the framework.
org.hck.pages
Each class file here encapsulates the methods and elements of a particular webpage.
org.hck.reports
Package contains classes related to ExtentReports initialisation and management.
org.hck.tests
Package contains all the test cases that this framework needs to run.
org.hck.utils
Package contains classes related to Utilities.
